# Shared Packages

Pure TypeScript libraries — no I/O, no side effects.

| Package | Role |
|---------|------|
| `history-models` | JSON schemas/types for history repo data |
| `history-publisher` | Pure functions for history repo file updates |

## Rules

- Action I/O (filesystem, GitHub API) stays in `src/`, not here.
- Export from each package's `src/index.ts`.
- Import via `@actions-insights/history-models` / `@actions-insights/history-publisher` (path aliases in root `tsconfig.json`).
- When changing shared models, add or update tests in root `test/`.
